{"type": "article", "id": 44198, "title": "腾讯做了“黄皮子洞”版COSTA ，华为海外广告又一支 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2017-08-17T05:19:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 12256, "name": "嘻哈"}, {"id": 1437, "name": "腾讯"}, {"id": 6329, "name": "蒙牛"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170817143458ZeDyFwWg4IhAdmMv.png", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">又是跨界</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #3e3e3e} span.s1 {font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #323333} span.s2 {font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 16.0px Arial; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; font-kerning: none; color: #000000} span.s5 {font: 14.0px 'Lucida Grande'; font-kerning: none; color: #000000} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"https://qy.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/wap_getnewsmsg?action=get&amp;__biz=MzA4OTIyNDQ1MQ==&amp;mixuin=MjU0MjY0MzI4MzMwOTU5ODU0OQ==&amp;mid=10001025&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=bf44636dc59b04237aa1bdb0a239412a&amp;scene=1\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>腾讯视频在三里屯 3.3 大厦打造了一家名为“黄皮子洞”的 COSTA 主题门店</b></a>。来看图。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817124249k2zB75W0Ybt6Gilo.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817124301Lj7U16pt4ax0siNC.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708171243216EpQBo9kmNHygTGh.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708171243333sYpvNW8tf1mIeuP.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.778125\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p>为了给旗下出品的《鬼吹灯之黄皮子坟》造势，腾讯视频和乐高、纯 K、良品铺子等做过一系列跨界合作。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817124424vVYeL7gTD8u30GMd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">《鬼吹灯之黄皮子坟》X 乐高</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817124450QXRFYMGN7Wz3qKPU.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">《鬼吹灯之黄皮子坟》X 乐高</figcaption></figure></div><h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的广告</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939} span.s1 {font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; font-kerning: none; color: #000000} span.s2 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/08/16/the-new-ad-of-meizu-note-6/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>中国又嘻哈了，魅族找“小青龙”拍广告</b></a>。魅蓝 Note 6 的主题广告 MV 由“中国有嘻哈”的说唱歌手“小青龙”演绎。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=q05383ikekf&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 45.0px; font: 34.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><b><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/41843\" rel=\"nofollow\">又一支华为海外广告出街，这次讲“关于跟踪”。</a></b>华外在海外市场的广告一直做的不错，这支片子讲述了四个拙劣的黑衣人跟踪女主的故事，看起来一点不专业，还有点滑稽。至于他们的真实身份，嘘，看到最后你就明白了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=h0529xpvanw&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 45.0px; font: 34.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>公司有啥大事发生</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #b22222} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"http://www.adquan.com/post-2-41848.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>历时 7 年，加多宝和王老吉的“红罐之争”终告落幕</b></a>。最高人民法院终审判决认为，广药集团与加多宝公司对涉案“红罐王老吉凉茶”包装装潢权益的形成均作出了重要贡献，双方可在不损害他人合法利益的前提下，共同享有“红罐王老吉凉茶”包装装潢的权益。从配方、包装到文案“玩火”这两家都抢过，说实话，买凉茶的时候真有人分得清吗？</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3NDA3NzQ0Mg==&amp;mid=2651730411&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1b69ef2481f962189df6a68f44c2006a&amp;chksm=f0e31386c7949a9074b91fa8412efa56bea08c99d5a3f3b0bc00e2152969c31964f3628a8f22&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0816WBhjOJfPv4iUIIPkdK9b&amp;key=ec2bfb07aacba687a0ad5457d62f3352de651ae69be22bb433a16d029118a0448b078bc8e13c7c59ff6b43e3936abc5cc75957ac083b150612ccffb84d5a63e438035049beed1e79d2bcb2747a7e87f0&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.10.5+build(14F2511)&amp;version=11000006&amp;pass_ticket=qa5IOJCohKCa%2FXTpBYSuwubx%2BJ4888KGJwssCcgZuZejjYBxnyKVRP7F4mZmNSto\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>凯络媒体拿到了蒙牛的全部媒介策划与 OTV 购买，这是今年国内最大型的媒介比稿之一</b></a>。之前有分析说蒙牛乳业的媒介业务花费大约在 20 亿人民币左右，此前阳狮媒体旗下的突破传播北京办公室负责蒙牛的媒介事宜已经超过十年。目前暂时不清楚传统TV的购买会由哪家来负责。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NDczMzgxMQ==&amp;mid=2662472829&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=014082eeafe65cd303fcffc0e84ce4b1&amp;chksm=bdc5f7e18ab27ef7e2e67480072a24ccb105ffe6d70757105e5cf1b1e4d9f1a273109ee0b2f0&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0816HifqccUtUtuEMc4gcrEK&amp;key=c624e15db90bf06699d4ece4bfe4e549600e254622590699d3dcfb6b1e1ed086d06dada393cdc12a0cd10ee02788ba6aacde2711c5c697a95be0fa3f5d3f3c7d06ef9bdaae23f680ee26b45475157eb1&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.10.5+build(14F2511)&amp;version=11000006&amp;pass_ticket=qa5IOJCohKCa%2FXTpBYSuwubx%2BJ4888KGJwssCcgZuZejjYBxnyKVRP7F4mZmNSto\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>腾讯 2017 年第二季度总收入为人民币 566.06 亿元，比去年同期增长 59%</b></a>。其中，网络广告业务的收入同比增长 55%。社交及其他广告收入增长 61% 至人民币 60.71 亿元，占网络广告收入的 59.8%。该项增长主要反映来自微信（主要是微信朋友圈及微信公众账号）及其他移动端应用的广告收入增长。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170817130203T92djnuBSwcvP6yX.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666917\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>"}